<p style="padding:0px 20px 0px 40px;">A member should utilize the Club Units from 2015 units before end of December 2017 – i.e. three year window period 1/1/2015 – end 2017. A reservation cannot be confirmed in 2017 for occupation in the following year to avoid forfeiting Club Units from 2015.</p>
<p style="padding:0px 20px 0px 40px;">A member with a two (2) year window period may accumulate any unused Club Units for one (1) year, so as to carry such Club Units forward for use during the following year, provided that such Club Units may not be accumulated for a period in excess of two (2) years. The first year's units have to be utilized before the end of the second year. For example:</p>
